{
  "stem": "20800.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], there was others, and we went-- I have even in paper, newspaper, my name.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went around kibbutz and all Jewish organization and give them a concert, and mostly in Jewish, you see?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was my-- but I, I got good money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For my two concerts, I got more than my husband for a whole month in working, but that's besides the point.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we just stayed in Poland, and stayed in Poland till-- Did you experience any antisemitism in Poland?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first thing, why I come here, it was antisemitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they, they couldn't say I'm Jew if I don't say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But one day, my daughter went to first grade at school and come with a cry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mom!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They told me, Jew, go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I heard this, that was-- I have heard this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stay in the queue, and they say-- and they said and Polish, Jew is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Normal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I could feel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes I just put it away, like-- but sometimes I couldn't take it, and I just tell, what did I do to you!",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Why?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it bugs me very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the reason I said-- when my daughter come home with a cry, I said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're not going to stay here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's for sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then my husband-- my husband said he got in Australia a distant cousin, but he doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He knows only name, but he doesn't know where is he.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I got-- had a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had children the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to go to the park with them and this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said, I'm going to Australia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
